1.title: Episode #3.1
1.plot: Babies are shaking up the lives of new and expectant parents. Autumn & Matthew face a challenge bigger than raising a baby on their tiny boat. Jamielynn wants boyfriend Matt to stop behaving like he's single. Aly & Josh endure a parent's worst nightmare.

2.title: Holy Triplets
2.plot: Autumn & Matthew try to set aside their differences for the sake of their baby. After 3 miscarriages, Julia & Ryan pray she can carry their triplets to term. Matt shocks Jamielynn with career news. Aly struggles with a side effect from her past cancer.

3.title: Pregnant 8 Months, Together for 9
3.plot: An unexpected turn complicates Julia's pregnancy with the triplets. Jamielynn's water breaks weeks early. Mariah & Raymond, together only 9 months, meet each other's families for the first time. Autumn's mom worries about the baby living on the boat.

4.title: Overdue and Overwhelmed
4.plot: Jamielynn juggles caring for a newborn & toddler alone when Matt returns to work. Overdue Autumn tries everything to avoid being induced. Julia & Ryan navigate the heartbreak of NICU life. As Mariah's due date approaches, her fear of child birth grows.

2.title: Quadrupe Trouble
2.plot: Ashley gives birth to quads twelve weeks early. Unprepared Mars and Doug struggle with their new roles. Kristina is torn between wanting to work and care for her baby in Brooklyn. We meet Destiny and Sal, a duo with fiery, battling families.

3.title: Maybe It's Time for the Epidural
3.plot: Ashley and Tyson bring their 8-week-old quadruplets home from the hospital. Doug and Mars have an added problem as they struggle caring for Sofia. Destiny gives birth to baby Capri. Kristina goes back to work for the first time since having Lincoln.

4.title: When Grandparents Attack
4.plot: Tyson returns to work, leaving Ashley to care for all 4 babies on her own. Destiny spars with Sal's parents over whether to baptize Capri. To save their relationship, Doug and Mars try couples therapy. Kristina and Jason struggle to expand their business.

5.title: Daycare Drama
5.plot: Destiny interviews nannies despite objections from family members. Chaos erupts when Ashley takes on a quad photo shoot without Tyson. Kristina considers putting Lincoln in daycare to prioritize her business. Doug flees to Florida after a fight with Mars.

6.title: Redefining "Having It All"
6.plot: Ashley and Tyson celebrate the girls' first birthday with an emotional trip to the NICU. Doug locates Mars and pleads for forgiveness. Sal and Destiny struggle to break away from their overbearing moms. Kristina must choose between work and family.

1.title: Broken Water, Broken Hearts
1.plot: Surprise pregnancies turn 3 couples' lives upside down. Krystal & Jarrel argue over their baby's paternity until Krystal goes into labor. Aly & Josh uproot their lives to grow their family. Doug & Mars are still volatile even though their baby is now 2.

2.title: Return of the Quads
2.plot: Jarrel won't talk custody with Krystal without a DNA test. Aly's allergic reaction during labor makes her high-risk pregnancy more dangerous. The quads are back and busting out of their house. Brooke, a pregnant wrestler, is terrified of giving birth.

3.title: Secret DNA Test
3.plot: As Aly & Josh's surrogate birth mom goes into labor, they worry she'll have difficulty giving up the baby. Jarrel does a paternity test on Boston without telling Krystal. Brooke goes into labor three weeks early. Mars gives Doug an ultimatum.

4.title: The Ultimate Heartbreak
4.plot: Aly & Josh get difficult news from the birth mom of the baby they're adopting. Jarrel gets results of the DNA test. Brooke has a scare with the baby on the day she brings him home from the hospital. Tyson is left alone with the quads for the first time.

5.title: I Think I'm Pregnant Again
5.plot: Aly & Josh pray that their birth mom will change her mind. Brooke takes steps to return to pro wrestling after Weston quits his job. Ashley & Tyson stress as they decide if they should build a house. A shocked Mars thinks she might be pregnant.

6.title: Pregnancy Test Result
6.plot: Mars gets her pregnancy test results. Krystal has second thoughts about Jarrel bringing their baby to meet his friends. Brooke gets concerned when she's Weston's new office space. Ashley & Tyson's move has them scrambling to make money at a big expo.

7.title: Pump and Dump
7.plot: Mars & Doug have a blowout after she meets his ex-wife. Aly & Josh have a scare when they return home. On her first night out since the birth, Brooke has to pump breastmilk in a bar. In order to make money, Ashley & Tyson have to send the quads home.

8.title: Turning the Babies
8.plot: Furious, Jarrel decides he is done with Krystal for good. Aly & Josh adjust to their new life at home with three babies. Brooke gets a tryout with her old wrestling bosses. Mars turns the tables on Doug and gets the attention of another man.

9.title: Back in the Ring
9.plot: Brooke gets back in the ring to see if she can wrestle again. Mars & Doug go to counseling to save the relationship before Mars' ultimatum expires. Aly approaches a crucial milestone in her cancer recovery. The quads visit the doctor who delivered them.

10.title: A Life Changing Question
10.plot: Two parents get surprises that change their lives. Brooke has her first wrestling match as a mom. Krystal relies on a father figure for Boston. Aly gets her diagnosis. The Gardners make a decision about their house. Mars gets an answer to her ultimatum.

-1.title: A Paralyzed Mother's Story
-1.plot: Quadriplegic Rachelle Friedman Chapman, the 'paralyzed bride', defies the odds by having her own child.

imdb.title: Rattled
plot: _Rattled_ (qv) explores the scary, exhilarating, frustrating, joyful and ultimately life-changing experience of parenthood.::TLC
